window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><b>Powerful monsters and magic. A new caretaker has arrived. Welcome to the Sanctuary....</b></p> <p>After disaster brought me to Stonefield Sanctuary, I figured it was all a dream.</p> <p>It’s not every day you discover you’ve been selected to become the next caretaker of a preserve full of monster girls, fantasy creatures, and magic I’d only seen in games or read about in books.</p> <p>Now, the residents need help, and I’m the only one who can save them.</p> <p>I’ll need to earn the trust of my allies, including the beautiful monster girls at my side, to complete quests, build defenses, grow stronger, and defeat our enemies.</p> <p>Only then will I become the most powerful caretaker any sanctuary has ever seen.</p> <p><b>Time to get started.</b></p> <p>I’ve got cards to collect, skills to develop, a town to build, monster girls to rescue, and mysteries to solve.</p> <p>All I have to do is ensure I survive long enough to do so.</p> <p><b>This series includes:</b></p> <ul> <li>Progression fantasy</li> <li>Town building/crafting</li> <li>Card collecting</li> <li>Pets</li> <li>Light LitRPG/GameLit mechanics</li> <li><i>Isekai</i>/portal fantasy</li> <li>Monster girls</li> <li>Unconventional relationships</li> <li>Non-fade-to-black</li> <li>Magic and sword fights</li> <li>Strong language</li> </ul>"; 
